{"tid":1037194,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【大時代】中國市民開證卷戶口期間被打尖，引發毆打事件","createTime":"2019-02-25T18:15:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-26T06:03:54.000Z","uid":66271,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"16aec30e6e752df9e528cc3a226e4fe17a2cfc95","tid":1037194,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T18:15:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.jrjimg.cn/2019/02/cms_20190225134002176.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.jrjimg.cn%2F2019%2F02%2Fcms_20190225134002176.jpg&h=da6636ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n市傳內地市民為開戶在證券行外排隊期間，因有人「打尖」引發鬥毆事件，可見資本市場的熱熾。　　<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n券商板塊在多重利好之下，繼３２隻券商股上周五（２２日）漲停後，目前再有２４隻券商漲停，包括中信建投（滬：６０１０６６）、中國銀河（滬：６０１８８１）、華泰（滬：６０１６８８）、中信證券（滬：６０００３０）及招商證券（滬：６００９９９）。（ｅｙ）"},{"pid":"38eceb4ab95eece4943d2ace9e2934cf5f508c6a","tid":1037194,"uid":198008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T00:43:59.000Z","msg":"會唔會重演15年<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f88116f66bb1d82a9e2657577bfdd0333f4abfe","tid":1037194,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"38eceb4ab95eece4943d2ace9e2934cf5f508c6a","tid":1037194,"uid":198008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T00:43:59.000Z","msg":"會唔會重演15年<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T03:19:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edcadd35480d79d9bdce9358392258d1e32ff420","tid":1037194,"uid":168716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T06:03:54.000Z","msg":"係咪又可以投淡了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}